### Options

{{{optionsTable}}}

- `name`: Unique tokenizer name. Generated tokens retain it so the parser can dispatch later phases
  to the same tokenizer.

- `priority`: Processing priority. Tokenizers with higher values run first. During block matching,
  a higher-priority tokenizer can interrupt a lower-priority tokenizer.{{#if hasListOptions}}

- `enableTaskListItem`: Enable GFM task list items.

- `emptyItemCouldNotInterruptedTypes`: Node types that an empty list item cannot interrupt.{{/if}}
